{"tw": {"3664240": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Norn's Dine", "steam_appid": 3664240, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4335530], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事簡介◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角「旭」是居住在防衛都市「阿斯嘉特」的青年。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「旭」從祖母那邊繼承了以「命運」女神之名命名的餐館《Norn's Dine》，以高超的廚藝與親切的性格，逐漸成為街坊間小有名氣的人氣主廚。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這正是「命運的餐桌」── 一段「旭」在《Norn's Dine》中，與來訪之人邂逅、編織出的「命運」的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆關於遊戲◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/dba510551c3f145cd4954699de5d38d6.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/dba510551c3f145cd4954699de5d38d6.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=567 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Norn's Dine》是一款可以與各種個性鮮明的角色們，不斷互動、加深交流的18禁BL文字冒險遊戲。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過選擇並接待不同的來店角色，可以提升角色的好感度，解鎖獨特的專屬劇情。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著羈絆加深、劇情層層推進，也能觀賞到與親密對象之間，令人臉紅心跳的H場景……！   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情約 20 萬字，每位可攻略角色都有約 10 萬字以上的專屬劇情。 日常事件 CG 與 H 事件 CG 的總數為原畫 59 張（+ 大量差分），份量非常充足！ 預計通關一條路線的遊玩時間大約為 8～10 小時。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★steam版本會有對性器的打碼處理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☆第一彈可攻略的角色為： 弗雷戴里克、奧爾菲歐、朱利奧、士道 此四位角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 各角色的詳細介紹請參考官方網站。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之後的另外四位角色將會在後續的追加 DLC 中依序販售。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b0a2fcd66ebbbda9eb8c529f66cd72d0.avif?t=1772364288\" width=1200 height=676 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆人物介紹◆</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Vol.1　可攻略角色</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/64c743da795188cc4326c85f4db798aa.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/64c743da795188cc4326c85f4db798aa.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【弗雷戴里克】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齢：35歳 　種族：人間 　職業：騎士團團長 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：190cm 　體重：110kg </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守護阿斯嘉特的騎士團團長。性格剛毅，能力與品格都極為適合擔任騎士。身為名門貴族的長子，卻與家人關係不佳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/9eed879725c203e43c51d38786dc9320.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/9eed879725c203e43c51d38786dc9320.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【奧爾菲歐】<u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：40歲　種族：獸人（虎）　職業：黑手黨老大</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：203cm　體重：150kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在暗中掌控阿斯嘉特的黑手黨首領。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然外表看起來兇惡，但其實十分喜愛小孩、心胸寬大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰鬥能力雖強，但硬要說的話更擅長以黑手黨實施組織型經濟犯罪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/6121724ade0e8d3b676d3616e22c05d9.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/6121724ade0e8d3b676d3616e22c05d9.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【士道】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：32歲　種族：半獸人（牛）　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：199cm　體重：125kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在倒下時被旭所救的牛型獸人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喪失了過往的記憶，充滿謎團。舉止顯得孩子氣，常表現出缺乏常識與倫理感的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/246867df8ae8303b3838d86466c20a19.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/246867df8ae8303b3838d86466c20a19.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【朱利歐】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：24歲　種族：人類　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：178cm　體重：80kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旭的青梅竹馬兼摯友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >待人隨和，言行輕浮卻十分看重情意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出身自崇尚戰鬥的部族，目前正處於修行之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/046ffc6b8928d3ae7cccc83e90d91b8f.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/046ffc6b8928d3ae7cccc83e90d91b8f.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【古蘭德】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：36歲　種族：魔人　職業：公會會長</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：188cm　體重：95kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被稱作魔人的特殊種族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現任冒險者公會的會長，年輕時也是身手不凡的冒險者。與弗雷戴里克是多年的舊識。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/d0efe171b63304b622c3d251195e85d0.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/d0efe171b63304b622c3d251195e85d0.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【利托】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：20歲　種族：半獸人（犬）　職業：店員</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：190cm　體重：100kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格溫和、心地善良的大型犬型半獸人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Norn's Dine負責接待與製作料理，總是帶著笑容、是店裡的氣氛製造者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/64c8f8c8f7cc889c102e87bd9373b6fb.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/64c8f8c8f7cc889c102e87bd9373b6fb.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【盧卡斯】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：28歲　種族：人類　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：185cm　體重：88kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自幼時便被旭的父母收養，兩人雖無血緣關係但卻如兄弟一般。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖並非沉默寡言，但不擅長表達情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/0778d6ecd5c40f498067c9759d84ae2d.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/0778d6ecd5c40f498067c9759d84ae2d.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【拉普拉斯】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：你覺得看起來像幾歲？　種族：就說了是秘密　職業：只要工作的話就輸了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：173cm　體重：70kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自稱吟遊詩人的青年，性格非常有問題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >總是突然出現在旭面前，留下耐人尋味的話後便消失無蹤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.apng?t=1772364288\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.poster.avif?t=1772364288\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>←姆魯姆魯</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事簡介◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角「旭」是居住在防衛都市「阿斯嘉特」的青年。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「旭」從祖母那邊繼承了以「命運」女神之名命名的餐館《Norn's Dine》，以高超的廚藝與親切的性格，逐漸成為街坊間小有名氣的人氣主廚。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這正是「命運的餐桌」── 一段「旭」在《Norn's Dine》中，與來訪之人邂逅、編織出的「命運」的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆關於遊戲◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/dba510551c3f145cd4954699de5d38d6.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/dba510551c3f145cd4954699de5d38d6.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=567 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Norn's Dine》是一款可以與各種個性鮮明的角色們，不斷互動、加深交流的18禁BL文字冒險遊戲。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過選擇並接待不同的來店角色，可以提升角色的好感度，解鎖獨特的專屬劇情。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著羈絆加深、劇情層層推進，也能觀賞到與親密對象之間，令人臉紅心跳的H場景……！   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主線劇情約 20 萬字，每位可攻略角色都有約 10 萬字以上的專屬劇情。 日常事件 CG 與 H 事件 CG 的總數為原畫 59 張（+ 大量差分），份量非常充足！ 預計通關一條路線的遊玩時間大約為 8～10 小時。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★steam版本會有對性器的打碼處理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☆第一彈可攻略的角色為： 弗雷戴里克、奧爾菲歐、朱利奧、士道 此四位角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 各角色的詳細介紹請參考官方網站。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之後的另外四位角色將會在後續的追加 DLC 中依序販售。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b0a2fcd66ebbbda9eb8c529f66cd72d0.avif?t=1772364288\" width=1200 height=676 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆人物介紹◆</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Vol.1　可攻略角色</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/64c743da795188cc4326c85f4db798aa.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/64c743da795188cc4326c85f4db798aa.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【弗雷戴里克】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齢：35歳 　種族：人間 　職業：騎士團團長 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：190cm 　體重：110kg </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守護阿斯嘉特的騎士團團長。性格剛毅，能力與品格都極為適合擔任騎士。身為名門貴族的長子，卻與家人關係不佳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/9eed879725c203e43c51d38786dc9320.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/9eed879725c203e43c51d38786dc9320.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【奧爾菲歐】<u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：40歲　種族：獸人（虎）　職業：黑手黨老大</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：203cm　體重：150kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在暗中掌控阿斯嘉特的黑手黨首領。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然外表看起來兇惡，但其實十分喜愛小孩、心胸寬大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰鬥能力雖強，但硬要說的話更擅長以黑手黨實施組織型經濟犯罪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/6121724ade0e8d3b676d3616e22c05d9.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/6121724ade0e8d3b676d3616e22c05d9.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【士道】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：32歲　種族：半獸人（牛）　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：199cm　體重：125kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在倒下時被旭所救的牛型獸人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喪失了過往的記憶，充滿謎團。舉止顯得孩子氣，常表現出缺乏常識與倫理感的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/246867df8ae8303b3838d86466c20a19.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/246867df8ae8303b3838d86466c20a19.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【朱利歐】 <u>※<strong>Vol.1　可攻略角色</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：24歲　種族：人類　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：178cm　體重：80kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旭的青梅竹馬兼摯友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >待人隨和，言行輕浮卻十分看重情意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出身自崇尚戰鬥的部族，目前正處於修行之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/046ffc6b8928d3ae7cccc83e90d91b8f.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/046ffc6b8928d3ae7cccc83e90d91b8f.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【古蘭德】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：36歲　種族：魔人　職業：公會會長</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：188cm　體重：95kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被稱作魔人的特殊種族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >現任冒險者公會的會長，年輕時也是身手不凡的冒險者。與弗雷戴里克是多年的舊識。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/d0efe171b63304b622c3d251195e85d0.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/d0efe171b63304b622c3d251195e85d0.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【利托】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：20歲　種族：半獸人（犬）　職業：店員</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：190cm　體重：100kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格溫和、心地善良的大型犬型半獸人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Norn's Dine負責接待與製作料理，總是帶著笑容、是店裡的氣氛製造者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/64c8f8c8f7cc889c102e87bd9373b6fb.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/64c8f8c8f7cc889c102e87bd9373b6fb.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【盧卡斯】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：28歲　種族：人類　職業：冒險者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：185cm　體重：88kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自幼時便被旭的父母收養，兩人雖無血緣關係但卻如兄弟一般。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖並非沉默寡言，但不擅長表達情感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/0778d6ecd5c40f498067c9759d84ae2d.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/0778d6ecd5c40f498067c9759d84ae2d.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【拉普拉斯】 <u>※<strong>追加下載包　可攻略角色</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：你覺得看起來像幾歲？　種族：就說了是秘密　職業：只要工作的話就輸了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：173cm　體重：70kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自稱吟遊詩人的青年，性格非常有問題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >總是突然出現在旭面前，留下耐人尋味的話後便消失無蹤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.apng?t=1772364288\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.poster.avif?t=1772364288\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>←姆魯姆魯</p>", "short_description": "由HIC所獻上的18禁文字冒險遊戲第一彈！  以「阿斯嘉特」為舞台，邂逅各個造訪《Norn's Dine》的魅力角色，加深與他們的羈絆，解鎖各自的專屬劇情！ 除了有超級豐富的角色劇情之外，也千萬別錯過每名角色人設繪師精心繪製的H場景！", "supported_languages": "英文, 繁體中文, 日文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/faefa74a85032c423c5774deb894de770972f937/header.jpg?t=1772364288", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/defa9fd01074433dc796721e9daa9ffeaab26cba/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1772364288", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/defa9fd01074433dc796721e9daa9ffeaab26cba/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1772364288", "website": "https://www.hichicgames.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10/11 64bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3-2100 / AMD FX-4300<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Intel HD Graphics 4000<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：10<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> </li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10/11 64bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5-4590 / AMD Ryzen 3 2200G<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 750 Ti / AMD Radeon R7 260X<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> </li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> macOS 10.13 High Sierra<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5 2.0GHz/Apple M1<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Intel HD Graphics 4000<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> macOS 10.15 Catalina<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5 2.5GHz以上 / Apple M1以降<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> AMD Radeon Pro 555/Apple M1 GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["HIC*"], "publishers": ["HIC*"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 84500, "final": 84500, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 845"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 68, "description": "自訂音量控制"}, {"id": 76, "description": "只需滑鼠選項"}, {"id": 74, "description": "遊玩無需快速反應"}, {"id": 79, "description": "隨時儲存"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 2 月 7 日"}}}}, "us": {"3664240": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Norn's Dine", "steam_appid": 3664240, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4335530], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Synopsis◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asahi, the protagonist, is a young man living in the defensive city of Asgard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He inherited his grandmother's restaurant “Norn's Dine”, named after the goddess of “destiny”, and spends his days as a chef who is well known for his skill and amiable personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is “Fate's Table” - the story of Asahi's “destiny” with the people she meets at Norn's Dine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆About the game◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/8bc4efe0e92c61f41a36d70477a5d0fb.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/8bc4efe0e92c61f41a36d70477a5d0fb.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=567 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Norn's Dine” is an 18-rated BL novel game in which players interact with a variety of unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By selecting the characters who visit the store, the likability level increases and unique episodes are released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you deepen your bond and have more episodes, you will be able to enjoy erotic scenes with the person you have become intimate with……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A visual novel with 59 original illustrations, and a sizable amount of text. Each route has roughly 8 to 10  hours of content! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐︎Genitalia are censored with mosaic effects in the Steam release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☆ The base game includes four routes in total: Frederick, Orfeo, Giulio, and Shidou. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOTE: Four additional characters will be added in the future as DLC. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View more details about each character on our official website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b0a2fcd66ebbbda9eb8c529f66cd72d0.avif?t=1772364288\" width=1200 height=676 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Character Introductions◆</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/e256de3dd424738d189f2dbc66cf421e.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/e256de3dd424738d189f2dbc66cf421e.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Frederick】　<strong><u>※vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：35　Race：Human   Occupation：Knight Commander</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：190cm　Weight：110kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The head of the knights who protect Asgard. Though he can be rather rigid, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >his abilities and character make him an exemplary knight. He is the eldest son of a </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >noble family, but has a strained relationship with his household.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/d0c45f77b19b910f1ea831c809a904f1.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/d0c45f77b19b910f1ea831c809a904f1.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Orfeo】　<strong><u>※vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：40　Race：Beastman（Tiger）Occupation：Mafia Boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：203cm　Weight：150kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The boss of a mafia faction that controls Asgard from the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He has a tough appearance, but deep down, he has a heart of gold and is quite fond of children.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While highly capable in combat, he is more of a black market mafioso.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/f6f5707564715aa95083db3a794a57b6.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/f6f5707564715aa95083db3a794a57b6.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Shido】　<strong><u>※vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：32　Race：Beastman（bull）Occupation：Adventurer（？）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：199cm　Weight：125kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious half-beast bull who Asahi found passed out. Due to his amnesia, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >he has no recollection of his past. His behavior is often compared to that of a child,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >lacking in common sense and moral awareness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/3191b19b9b565911e3df263aa4c14b3c.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/3191b19b9b565911e3df263aa4c14b3c.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Giulio】　<strong><u>※vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：24　Race：Human　Occupation：Adventurer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：178cm　Weight：100kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asahi's childhood friend. He’s friendly with everyone and often comes across as frivolous,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but he’s very compassionate. Comes from a tribe of warriors that hold battle in high regard, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and is currently undergoing rigorous training.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Additional DLC Character</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/3c89a0a12a48ba7987e4ec39c4354d62.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/3c89a0a12a48ba7987e4ec39c4354d62.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Grant】　<strong><u>※Additional DLC Character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：36　Race：Demon　Occupation：Guildmaster</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：188cm　Weight：95kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The master of the Adventurers' Guild who was a skilled adventurer himself</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in his younger days. An old friend of Frederick's.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b71380f4de8523392b1549576e0e7d60.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/b71380f4de8523392b1549576e0e7d60.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Rito】　<strong><u>※Additional DLC Character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：20　Race：half-beast（Dog）Occupation：Waiter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：190cm　Weight：100kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A gentle and kind-hearted half-beast whose appaearance resembles a large dog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He is in charge of cooking and serving the customers at Norn's Dine, always </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >wearing a smile and serving as a cheerful mood-maker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b333d77d9adae33273ea1d368aa523a1.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/b333d77d9adae33273ea1d368aa523a1.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Lucas】　<strong><u>※Additional DLC Character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：28　Race：Human　Occupation：Adventurer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：185cm　Weight：88kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An adventurer who was taken by Asahi's parents when they were both at a very young age, making them brothers by bond. He's not exactly mute, but he often struggles to express his emotions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/3aeee9e5f191d6606330cf2ed4df3dfc.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/3aeee9e5f191d6606330cf2ed4df3dfc.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span>【Laplace】　<strong><u>※Additional DLC Character</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Age：How old do you think I am?　Race：It's a secret!　Occupation：You work, you lose!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Height：173cm　Weight：70kg</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young man with a deeply problematic personality who calls himself a bard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He sometimes appears before Asahi, sings some cryptic words, and just as</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >suddenly, vanishes without a trace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.apng?t=1772364288\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/2f8530c330238b49d9bacf2167337158.poster.avif?t=1772364288\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>←Murmur</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/f553a9efa7c37a80632fe46b48250f6b.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=451 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Synopsis◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asahi, the protagonist, is a young man living in the defensive city of Asgard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He inherited his grandmother's restaurant “Norn's Dine”, named after the goddess of “destiny”, and spends his days as a chef who is well known for his skill and amiable personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is “Fate's Table” - the story of Asahi's “destiny” with the people she meets at Norn's Dine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆About the game◆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/8bc4efe0e92c61f41a36d70477a5d0fb.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras_big/8bc4efe0e92c61f41a36d70477a5d0fb.avif?t=1772364288 width=800 height=567 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Norn's Dine” is an 18-rated BL novel game in which players interact with a variety of unique characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By selecting the characters who visit the store, the likability level increases and unique episodes are released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you deepen your bond and have more episodes, you will be able to enjoy erotic scenes with the person you have become intimate with……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A visual novel with 59 original illustrations, and a sizable amount of text. Each route has roughly 8 to 10  hours of content! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐︎Genitalia are censored with mosaic effects in the Steam release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☆ The base game includes four routes in total: Frederick, Orfeo, Giulio, and Shidou. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOTE: Four additional characters will be added in the future as DLC. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View more details about each character on our official website.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/b0a2fcd66ebbbda9eb8c529f66cd72d0.avif?t=1772364288\" width=1200 height=676 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Character Introductions◆</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>vol.1 Selectable character</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3664240/extras/e256de3dd424738d189f2dbc66cf421e.avif?t=1772364288\" data-big-s